#Learning the basics of SQL
This lab is the practical demonstration of theory and hand-on learning in a RDMS simulated platform MySQL with the help of simple but comprehensive situation.

---


1. Create a table name student with the following attributes (data types are shown in the parenthesis): Roll No (Integer), Name (varchar(50)), Gender (Char), CGPA (Float)
MySQL code => CREATE TABLE student (
    RollNo INT PRIMARY KEY,
    Name VARCHAR(50),
    Gender CHAR(1),
    CGPA FLOAT
);

